Extension: Radiomics Criteria Settings

Official URL: https://build.fhir.org/ig/arkhn/arkhn-ig-osiris/StructureDefinition/radiomics-criteria-settings Version: 2.1.0
Draft as of 2024-03-21 Computable Name: RadiomicsCriteriaSettings

Radiomics Criteria Settings.

Summary

Complex Extension: Radiomics Criteria Settings.

  • code: Coding: An Extension
  • valueString: string: An Extension
  • code: Coding: An Extension
  • valueString: string: An Extension
  • localizationMethod: string: The field allows you to define whether the calculation method has been applied to the whole image (voxels of the image) or on a area of interest (ROI).
  • windowMatrix: base64Binary, boolean, canonical, code, date, dateTime, decimal, id, instant, integer, markdown, oid, positiveInt, string, time, unsignedInt, uri, url, uuid, Address, Age, Annotation, Attachment, CodeableConcept, Coding, ContactPoint, Count, Distance, Duration, HumanName, Identifier, Money, Period, Quantity, Range, Ratio, Reference, SampledData, Signature, Timing, ContactDetail, Contributor, DataRequirement, Expression, ParameterDefinition, RelatedArtifact, TriggerDefinition, UsageContext, Dosage, Meta: Matrix of the calculation window (ex. 5x5x5 voxels)
  • usedImageFilter: string: Method used to filter the images before calculation
  • usedImageFilterParameters: base64Binary, boolean, canonical, code, date, dateTime, decimal, id, instant, integer, markdown, oid, positiveInt, string, time, unsignedInt, uri, url, uuid, Address, Age, Annotation, Attachment, CodeableConcept, Coding, ContactPoint, Count, Distance, Duration, HumanName, Identifier, Money, Period, Quantity, Range, Ratio, Reference, SampledData, Signature, Timing, ContactDetail, Contributor, DataRequirement, Expression, ParameterDefinition, RelatedArtifact, TriggerDefinition, UsageContext, Dosage, Meta: Parameters of the method used to filter the images before the calculation
  • code: Coding: An Extension
  • valueString: string: An Extension
  • code: Coding: An Extension
  • valueString: string: An Extension
  • code: Coding: An Extension
  • valueDecimal: decimal: An Extension
  • bounds: string: Bounds in intensity to perform the discretization
  • code: Coding: An Extension
  • valueDecimal: decimal: An Extension
  • code: Coding: An Extension
  • valueDecimal: decimal: An Extension
  • boundsRangeOfValueAfterDiscretisation: string: Bounds of the intensity value after discretization
  • spatialResamplingMethod: string: Spatial resampling method: Bicubic spline|Tricubic spline|Lagrangian polynomial
  • spatialResamplingValues: string: Spatial resampling values: x, y, z
  • code: Coding: An Extension
  • valueString: string: An Extension

Summary

Complex Extension: Radiomics Criteria Settings.

  • code: Coding: An Extension
  • valueString: string: An Extension
  • code: Coding: An Extension
  • valueString: string: An Extension
  • localizationMethod: string: The field allows you to define whether the calculation method has been applied to the whole image (voxels of the image) or on a area of interest (ROI).
  • windowMatrix: base64Binary, boolean, canonical, code, date, dateTime, decimal, id, instant, integer, markdown, oid, positiveInt, string, time, unsignedInt, uri, url, uuid, Address, Age, Annotation, Attachment, CodeableConcept, Coding, ContactPoint, Count, Distance, Duration, HumanName, Identifier, Money, Period, Quantity, Range, Ratio, Reference, SampledData, Signature, Timing, ContactDetail, Contributor, DataRequirement, Expression, ParameterDefinition, RelatedArtifact, TriggerDefinition, UsageContext, Dosage, Meta: Matrix of the calculation window (ex. 5x5x5 voxels)
  • usedImageFilter: string: Method used to filter the images before calculation
  • usedImageFilterParameters: base64Binary, boolean, canonical, code, date, dateTime, decimal, id, instant, integer, markdown, oid, positiveInt, string, time, unsignedInt, uri, url, uuid, Address, Age, Annotation, Attachment, CodeableConcept, Coding, ContactPoint, Count, Distance, Duration, HumanName, Identifier, Money, Period, Quantity, Range, Ratio, Reference, SampledData, Signature, Timing, ContactDetail, Contributor, DataRequirement, Expression, ParameterDefinition, RelatedArtifact, TriggerDefinition, UsageContext, Dosage, Meta: Parameters of the method used to filter the images before the calculation
  • code: Coding: An Extension
  • valueString: string: An Extension
  • code: Coding: An Extension
  • valueString: string: An Extension
  • code: Coding: An Extension
  • valueDecimal: decimal: An Extension
  • bounds: string: Bounds in intensity to perform the discretization
  • code: Coding: An Extension

  • code: Coding: An Extension
  • valueDecimal: decimal: An Extension
  • boundsRangeOfValueAfterDiscretisation: string: Bounds of the intensity value after discretization
